To find the index of an item in the collection:
1) Use $index property 
2) To get index of parent element: use $parent.$index or use ng-init="parentIndex=$index"


	<ul>
		<li ng-repeat="i in arr track by $index"> {{$index+1}} </li>
		
	</ul>
	
	
	The below code will print "Hello" the number of times the size of arr.
	<ul>
		<li ng-repeat="i in arr track by $index"> Hello </li>
		
	</ul>